{"tid":2102124,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黃國桐公開endorse本土派，白鴿情何以堪","createTime":"2020-07-10T08:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T14:36:48.000Z","uid":3560,"like":88,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c3c03d799233e309260f3d81d91d8b76104c80bc","tid":2102124,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:56:00.000Z","msg":"嘩屌，啱啱見到黃國桐endorse九西本土派馮達浚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LAwj6zx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLAwj6zx.jpg&h=c3950dfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃國桐：「2019年的區選，我認識了馮達浚（Frankie）。透過他，我結交了另外一群有學識、理想和站在抗爭前線的年青人。大家交心，多次坦談香港前途。各人內心沉重，但互相承諾，不退縮、不變形，直至力盡倒下。<br />\n<br />\n泛民初選，所有候選人都標榜自己是抗爭，為下一代，為法治為民主。但能身體力行的人有多少？抗爭怎會沒有承擔，沒有犧牲！在捍衛的路上，你可曾見他們的蹤影？<br />\n<br />\n本土的年青人經已成長，再不需要任何濫竽充數的所謂『代言人』。就讓我們全票支持香港年輕理想的本土候選人馮達浚（Frankie）和他的團隊。」<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/frankiefung.hk/photos/a.436948740167745/864959047366710\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffrankiefung.hk%2Fphotos%2Fa.436948740167745%2F864959047366710&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumom5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=d00de02c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/frankiefung.hk/photos/a.436948740167745/864959047366710</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"green\">你叫民主黨情何以堪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e1ad54a6aef52f297d87869d1a258a73fb5a8316","tid":2102124,"uid":3560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:57:12.000Z","msg":"今晚旺角本土派造勢大會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2102020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2102020</a>"},{"pid":"277e2acbe1563abf530356af0f998a572bba8e87","tid":2102124,"uid":14494,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:58:14.000Z","msg":"桐叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b6732be063836cbca43f710510118a3649fafd","tid":2102124,"uid":38904,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:58:27.000Z","msg":"黃律師無論個樣定心態都唔似7張嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40569b9305f5d6b36bc6089e3a9d2e328f9ae6a6","tid":2102124,"uid":52802,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:58:59.000Z","msg":"連黃國桐都支持本土<br />\n你叫抗爭派情何以堪<br />\n即係何桂藍 aka立場姐姐之流<br />\n懇請大家支持本土<br />\n咁先對得住梁天琦同埋其他手足既理念<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新界東初選 有本土投本土<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fFCznS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fFCznS</a>"},{"pid":"da7d30de807a663ad98546ffe3c639a6605a88c9","tid":2102124,"uid":4846,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:59:26.000Z","msg":"桐叔型撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c112ee77d01516eb5ee74a24a754bd5e7b96849e","tid":2102124,"uid":3560,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"05b6732be063836cbca43f710510118a3649fafd","tid":2102124,"uid":38904,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:58:27.000Z","msg":"黃律師無論個樣定心態都唔似7張嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T08:59:40.000Z","msg":"警署瞓街幫手足保釋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出心出力出命啊桐叔"},{"pid":"f2ee0978ca99abe22220b12c531ffab08a41db55","tid":2102124,"uid":52802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da7d30de807a663ad98546f